 Charles; introduced the $1 \"Yankee\" watch in 1896, making timepieces affordable for working people worldwide.","number":1,"category":"career"},{"header":"Wife's murder-suicide at 55 Park Avenue, 1926","detail":"Robert and Roberta Ingersoll were separated when the tragedy occurred Dec 19, 1926. Roberta shot Wallace M. Probasco four times in her apartment at 55 Park Avenue, then took her own life with a gunshot to the breast. Probasco survived. The incident was widely reported nationally. The couple had no children.","body":"Roberta Ingersoll shot her companion Wallace Probasco then took her own life in her Park Avenue apartment, December 1926.","number":2,"category":"crime"}],"number_of_marriages":1,"cross_connections":[],"bio":{"display_name":"Robert Hawley Ingersoll","first_name":"Robert","middle_name":"Hawley","maiden_name":"Ingersoll","married_names":[]},"residence":{},"baptism":{},"research_tags":[],"research_sources":[],"documents":[],"naming_inspiration":[],"institutions":[],"landmarks":[],"artworks":[],"quotes":[],"military_service":[],"slug":"robert-ingersoll-1859"},"HD1715":{"id":"HD1715","has_descendants_documented":true,"classification":{"include_in_path_calculation":true,"generation_from_thomas":9,"descent_from_thomas_hooker":true,"descent_from_john_talcott":false,"is_thomas_descendant":true,"is_talcott_descendant":false,"is_easter_egg":false},"birth":{"year":1865},"death":{"year":1948},"parents":{"father_id":"HD1699","mother_id":"X00551"},"marriages":[{"spouse_id":"X00555","children_ids":["HD1733","HD1734"],"marriage_number":1}],"tags":[],"sources":[],"gender":"male","notable":{"is_notable":true,"notable_category":[],"notable_blurb":"Maker of the famous Ingersoll dollar watch","primary_url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Henry_Ingersoll"},"number_of_marriages":1,"cross_connections":[],"bio":{"display_name":"Charles Henry Ingersoll","first_name":"Charles","last_name":"Ingersoll","middle_name":"Henry","married_names":[]},"residence":{},"baptism